Screen loads with html and css and a start button
Once the user clicks the start button the game begins
A timer begins counting down from 30 seconds
The user has 30 seconds to select all/ or as many as they can answers
The user may only select one answer per question
If the timer hits 0 then the user will no longer be able to select answers and will have score tallied
Otherwise the player can click a done button which will tally users score
The tallied score will show answers correct, answers incorrect, and unanswered